                                                                                                       ('1cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-30003ef4a271', '<p>Bir filtre kullanarak, mapping y&ouml;ntemlerinin her biri i&ccedil;in manuel olarak yant eklemekten ka&ccedil;nabiliriz.</p>\n\n<h3><strong>OncePerRequestFilter Implement Etme</strong></h3>\n\n<p>&Ouml;zel bir filtre oluturmak i&ccedil;in ayrca soyut snf&nbsp;<code>OncePerRequestFilter</code>&nbsp;extend edilir ve filtreye <code>@Component</code>&nbsp;annotation ekleriz. Her response&#39;a bir header ayarlamak i&ccedil;in, <code>HttpServletResponse</code>&nbsp;interface&#39;inin <code>addHeader()</code> y&ouml;ntemini kullanlrz.</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\nimport org.springframework.web.filter.OncePerRequestFilter;\nimport javax.servlet.FilterChain;\nimport javax.servlet.ServletException;\nimport javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest;\nimport javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse;\nimport java.io.IOException;\n\n@Component\npublic class FirstFilter extends OncePerRequestFilter {\n@Override\nprotected void doFilterInternal(HttpServletRequest httpServletRequest, HttpServletResponse httpServletResponse, FilterChain filterChain)throws ServletException, IOException {\nhttpServletResponse.addHeader(\"Access-Control-Allow-Origin\", \"*\");\nfilterChain.doFilter(httpServletRequest, httpServletResponse);\n}\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>Implementing Filter Interface&nbsp;Implement Etme</strong></h3>\n\n<p>Ayrca <code>Filter</code>&nbsp;aray&uuml;z&uuml;n&uuml; uygulayabilir ve filtreye, onu tanmas i&ccedil;in <code>@Component</code> gibi Spring stereotiplerinden biriyle a&ccedil;klama ekleyebiliriz. Her yanta &ouml;zel balk ayarlamak i&ccedil;in,&nbsp;<code>HttpServletResponse</code>&nbsp;interface&#39;inin&nbsp;<code>addHeader()</code> y&ouml;ntemini kullanlr.</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\nimport javax.servlet.*;\nimport javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest;\nimport javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse;\nimport java.io.IOException;\n\n@Component\npublic class FirstFilter implements Filter {\n@Override\npublic void doFilter(ServletRequest request, ServletResponse response, FilterChain chain) throws IOException, ServletException{\nHttpServletRequest req = (HttpServletRequest) request;\nHttpServletResponse res = (HttpServletResponse) response;\nres.addHeader(\"Access-Control-Allow-Origin\", \"*\");\nchain.doFilter(req, res);\n}\n}</code></pre>', 'tum-responselara-header-ekleme', 'Tm response\'lara Header ekleme', '2cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-16144ef4a27d', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', 'header'),
                                                                                                       ('1cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-30004ef4a271', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>JPA (Java Persistence API) nedir?</strong></h2>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">JPA, Java nesnelerini ilikisel bir veritabanna elemek i&ccedil;in Java standarddr. JPA, ORM&nbsp;yaklamdr. Gelitirici, JPA araclyla, ilikisel veritabanlarndan Java nesnelerine crud(create/read/update/delete) ilemlerine izin verir. JPA, Java-EE ve Java-SE uygulamalarnda kullanlabilir. JPA bir spesifikasyondur ve &ccedil;eitli uygulamalar mevcuttur.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>ORM (Objet Relational Mapping) nedir?</strong></h2>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">ORM, tamamen Entity olarak adlandrlan d&uuml;z Java Nesneleri bi&ccedil;imindeki verileri temsil etmek ve bunlara erimekle ilgili olan JPA&#39;nn temelidir. Hibernate, EclipseLink ve Apache OpenJPA, Hibernate&#39;in daha pop&uuml;ler olduu ve yaygn olarak kullanld JPA uygulamalarndan bazlardr.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Hibernate nedir?</strong></h2>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Hibernate, Java ortamlar i&ccedil;in bir ORM &ccedil;&ouml;z&uuml;m&uuml;d&uuml;r. Hibernate, uygulama etki alan nesnelerini ilikisel veritaban tablolaryla elemek i&ccedil;in bir &ccedil;er&ccedil;eve salayan Java tabanl bir ORM aracdr. Hibernate, JPA&#39;nn bir referans uygulamasn salar ve bu, onu gevek birletirme avantajlaryla ORM arac olarak m&uuml;kemmel bir se&ccedil;im haline getirir.&nbsp; Hibernate, Java tabanl bir ORM teknolojisidir.<img src=\"/upload/files/orm_example.png\" style=\"height:188px; width:800px\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Buraya kadar yazlanlardan yola &ccedil;karak JPA (Java Persistence Api) &lsquo;n bir standart, Hibernate&rsquo;in ise bir JPA uygulamas olduunu aklmzdan &ccedil;karmayalm.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Spring Data JPA nedir?</strong></h2>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Spring Data ailesinin bir &uuml;yesi olan&nbsp;Spring Data JPA,&nbsp;JPA tabanl repository&#39;lerin&nbsp;kolayca uygulanmasn kolaylatrr. Bu mod&uuml;l, JPA tabanl veri eriim katmanlar i&ccedil;in gelimi destek verir.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Spring Data sanld aksine Hibernate gibi bir JPA uygulamas deildir. Sadece JPA uygulamamzn en &uuml;st katmanna ekstra soyut bir katman ekleyen bir k&uuml;t&uuml;phanedir.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Veri eriim teknolojilerini kullanan Spring destekli uygulamalar oluturmay kolaylatrr. Bir uygulamann veri eriim katmann uygulamak, uzun s&uuml;redir k&uuml;lfetli olmutur. Basit sorgular y&uuml;r&uuml;tmek, sayfalandrma ve denetleme yapmak i&ccedil;in &ccedil;ok fazla standart kod yazlmaldr.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Spring Data JPA, &ccedil;abay ger&ccedil;ekten ihtiya&ccedil; duyulan miktara indirerek veri eriim katmanlarnn uygulanmasn &ouml;nemli &ouml;l&ccedil;&uuml;de iyiletirmeyi ama&ccedil;lamaktadr. Bir gelitirici olarak, &ouml;zel metodlarda dahil olmak &uuml;zere,&nbsp;repository interface&#39;ler&nbsp;yazarz ve Spring, uygulamay otomatik tanr.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Spring Data JPA vs Hibernate</strong></h2>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Spring Data JPA kullanarak aadaki CrudRepository uygulamasn d&uuml;&uuml;nelim:</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">import bookservice.model.Author;\nimport org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository;\n\npublic interface AuthorRepository extends CrudRepository {}</code></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">CrudRepository aray&uuml;z&uuml;n&uuml; basit&ccedil;e genileterek Spring, aadaki depo y&ouml;ntemlerini otomatik olarak uygulayacaktr:</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">save()\nsaveAll()\nfindById()\nexistsById()\nfindAll()\nfindAllById()\ncount()\ndeleteById()\ndelete()\ndeleteAll()</code></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Nesnelerin veritabannda kalmasn son derece kolaylatryor...</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">Author author = new Author();\nrepo.save(author); //save to database\nList authors = repo.findAll(); //find all authors</code></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Spring Data JPA kullanmasaydk, nesneleri veritabannda kalc hale getirmek i&ccedil;in daha fazla standart kod yazmamz gerekirdi ...</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">EntityManagerFactory emfactory = Persistence.createEntityManagerFactory(\"Hibernate\");\n\nEntityManager entitymanager = emfactory.createEntityManager();\nentitymanager.getTransaction().begin();\n\nAuthor author = new Author();\n\nentitymanager.persist(author);\nentitymanager.getTransaction().commit();\n\nentitymanager.close();\nemfactory.close();</code></pre>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Entity Manager, ilemleri ger&ccedil;ekletirme ve kapatma ile ilgili kullanldna&nbsp;dikkat edin? Bu, Spring Data JPA&#39;nn ka&ccedil;nmaya yardmc olduu kod t&uuml;r&uuml;d&uuml;r.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Spring Data JPA, bir JPA salaycs ile &ccedil;almay kolaylatran bir dizi bamllktr. Hibernate, birka&ccedil; JPA salaycsndan biridir. Bu, Spring Data JPA&#39;y Hibernate&#39;i kullanmadan kullanabileceiniz anlamna gelir.</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Diyelim ki uygulamamz i&ccedil;in spring + hibernate kullanyoruz. Artk hibernate&#39;in SessionFactory&#39;sini kullanarak crud ilemler i&ccedil;in dao aray&uuml;z&uuml;ne ve uygulamasna ihtiyacmz var. &Ccedil;alan snf i&ccedil;in dao snf yazdnz varsayalm daha sonra uygulamamzda baka herhangi bir varlk i&ccedil;in benzer ilem yazmamz gerekebilir. Yani burada g&ouml;rebileceimiz &ccedil;ok sayda ortak kod var. imdi Spring data jpa, repositoryleri(crudrepository, jparepository) genileterek dao aray&uuml;zlerini tanmlamamza izin veriyor, b&ouml;ylece &ccedil;alma zamannda size dao uygulamas salyor. Artk dao uygulamas yazmanza gerek yok. spring data jpa bu ekilde hayatnz kolaylatryor.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>SONU&Ccedil;</strong></h2>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Hibernate, Java nesnelerini ilikisel veritaban tablolaryla eleyen bir JPA salaycs ve ORM&#39;dir. Spring Data JPA, JPA salaycs ile &ccedil;almay daha az ayrntl hale getiren bir soyutlamadr. Spring Data JPA&#39;y kullanarak Hibernate gibi bir JPA salaycsnn y&ouml;netiminde yer alan bir&ccedil;ok standart kodu ortadan kaldrabilirsiniz.</p>', 'hibernate-vs-spring-data-jpa', 'Hibernate vs Spring Data JPA', '2cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-16144ef4a27d', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', 'Hibernate;Spring Data JPA'),
                                                                                                       ('1cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-30005ef4a271', '<p>Spring Boot JDBC, JPA/Hibernate, JOOQ gibi SQL tabanl veri eriim teknolojileri ile &ccedil;almay kolaylatrr.&nbsp;DataSource, pool kabiliyeti, transactionManager, JdbcTemplate, NamedParameterJdbcTemplate gibi noktalarda otomatik konfig&uuml;rasyon salar. Aktive etmek i&ccedil;in jdbc veya data-jpa starter&#39;na ihtiya&ccedil; vardr</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n  &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n  &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-data-jpa&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>DataSource Konfig&uuml;rasyonu</strong></h3>\n\n<p>Spring Boot veritaban balantlarn y&ouml;netmek i&ccedil;in javax.sql.DataSource tipinde bir bean&#39; otomatik olarak tanmlamaktadr Veritaban balant ayarlar dataSource bean&#39;ine &ouml;zel property&#39;ler ile yaplr</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.datasource.url=jdbc:h2:tcp://localhost/~/test\nspring.datasource.username=sa\nspring.datasource.password=\nspring.datasource.driver-class-name=org.h2.Driver</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>Embedded DB Destei</strong></h3>\n\n<p>Gelitirme s&uuml;recinde veriyi hafzada tutarak &ccedil;alan g&ouml;m&uuml;l&uuml; veritabanlar ile &ccedil;almak daha pratik olmaktadr. Veri kalc olarak kadedilmedii i&ccedil;in uygulama her baladnda populate edilmekte, uygulama sonlandnda da kaybedilmektedir. Spring Boot H2, HSQL, Derby g&ouml;m&uuml;l&uuml; veritabanlar ile &ccedil;almay destekler.&nbsp;G&ouml;m&uuml;l&uuml; veritaban konfig&uuml;rasyonunun otomatik olarak ger&ccedil;ekleebilmesi i&ccedil;in hem g&ouml;m&uuml;l&uuml; veritaban k&uuml;t&uuml;phanesine, hem de jdbc veya data-jpa starter&#39;larndan birisine ihtiya&ccedil; vardr.</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">&lt;dependencies&gt;\n	&lt;dependency&gt;\n		&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n		&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-data-jpa&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n	&lt;/dependency&gt;\n	&lt;dependency&gt;\n		&lt;groupId&gt;com.h2database&lt;/groupId&gt;\n		&lt;artifactId&gt;h2&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n		&lt;scope&gt;runtime&lt;/scope&gt;\n	&lt;/dependency&gt;\n&lt;/dependencies&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>H2 Web Console</strong></h3>\n\n<p>Spring Boot, H2&#39;nin web console&#39;unu otomatik olarak devreye sokar. Bunun i&ccedil;in;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Gelitirilen uygulamann web tabanl olmas,</li>\n	<li>H2&#39;nin classpath&#39;de olmas,</li>\n	<li>Spring Boot Dev Tools&#39;un kullanlmas</li>\n	<li>Dev Tools kullanlmasa da H2 console devreye alnabilir.\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.h2.console.enabled=true</code></pre>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Default path&#39;i /h2-console&#39;dur, deitirilebilir.\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.h2.console.path=/h2-console</code></pre>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>Connection Pool Kabiliyeti</strong></h3>\n\n<p>Spring Boot &uuml;retim ortamlar i&ccedil;in &ldquo;pooling&rdquo; kabiliyeti de salamaktadr. Default olarak HikariCP tercih edilir. kinci olarak classpath&#39;de Tomcat-Jdbc&#39;ye<br />\nbaklr. &Uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;nc&uuml; olarak Commons DBCP aranr. Son olarak da Commons DBCP2 tercih edilir.</p>\n\n<p>stenirse bu algortima uygulamaya g&ouml;re &ouml;zelletirilebilir.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.datasource.type=com.zaxxer.hikari.HikariDataSource</code></pre>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Her bir pooling algoritmasnn kendine ait property&#39;leri de mevcuttur.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.datasource.tomcat.*\nspring.datasource.hikari.*\nspring.datasource.dbcp2.*</code></pre>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>JNDI veya Custom DataSource</strong></h3>\n\n<p>Spring Boot uygulamas bir uygulama sunucusuna deploy edilecek ise JNDI &uuml;zerinden bu sunucudaki dataSource&#39;u da kullanmas salanabilir</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.datasource.jndi-name=java:comp/env/TestDB</code></pre>\n\n<p>stenirse tamamen uygulamaya &ouml;zel bir dataSource bean tanm da yaplabilir. Bu durumda Spring Boot dataSource ve pooling konfig&uuml;rasyonunda tamamen devre d kalacaktr.</p>\n\n<h3><strong>JDBC&nbsp;ile &Ccedil;almak</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>JDBC ile &ccedil;almak i&ccedil;in jdbc-starter&#39;na ihtiya&ccedil; vardr.</li>\n	<li>Spring Boot <strong>JdbcTemplate</strong> ve <strong>NamedParameterJdbcTemplate</strong> bean&#39;larn otomatik olarak tanmlar.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Repository\npublic class OwnerDaoJdbcImpl implements OwnerDao {\n	@Autowired\n	private JdbcTemplate jdbcTemplate;\n	@Autowired\n	private NamedParameterJdbcTemplate namedParameterJdbcTemplate;\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>JPA/Hibernate ile &Ccedil;almak</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>JPA ile &ccedil;alabilmek i&ccedil;in data-jpa starter&#39;na ihtiya&ccedil; vardr.</li>\n	<li>Spring Boot JPA destei Spring Data projesi &uuml;zerine kuruludur.</li>\n	<li><strong>EntityManagerFactory</strong> bean tanm otomatik olarak yaplr.</li>\n	<li>Spring Boot dorudan Hibernate &uuml;zerinden &ccedil;almay desteklemedii i&ccedil;in SessionFactory bean tanm mevcut deildir.</li>\n	<li>JPA/Hibernate property&#39;leri <strong>application.properties</strong> i&ccedil;erisinden uygulamaya g&ouml;re &ouml;zelletirilebilir.\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.dialect=org.hibernate.dialect.H2Dialect\nspring.jpa.properties.hibernate.show_sql=true\nspring.jpa.properties.hibernate.format_sql=true\nspring.jpa.properties.hibernate.use_sql_comments=true\n</code></pre>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>JPA Auto Scan Kabiliyeti</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Entity snflarn tespit etmek i&ccedil;in @EnableAutoConfiguration veya @SpringBootApplication anotasyonuna sahip snfn bulunduu paket ve alt paketleri taranr.</li>\n	<li>Benzer bi&ccedil;imde Spring Data Repository veya CrudRepository aray&uuml;zlerinden t&uuml;reyen uygulamaya &ouml;zel aray&uuml;zler de otomatik olarak tespit edilmektedir</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>JPA ile Otomatik ema Y&ouml;netimi</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Sadece g&ouml;m&uuml;l&uuml; veritaban kullanm durumunda JPA ile veritaban otomatik olarak yaratlacaktr.</li>\n	<li>Connection tipi H2, HSQLDB, DERBY ise g&ouml;m&uuml;l&uuml; veritaban olarak kabul edilir.</li>\n	<li>G&ouml;m&uuml;l&uuml; olmayan veritaban kullanmnda da bu &ouml;zellii aktive etmek i&ccedil;in,\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=create-drop</code></pre>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Bu tanm aadaki tanm her zaman ezer,\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.jpa.generate-ddl=true</code></pre>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>Open EntityManagerin View</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Spring Boot Hibernate ile &ccedil;alrken lazy hatalarnn &ouml;n&uuml;ne ge&ccedil;mek i&ccedil;in default olarak OpenEntityManagerInViewInterceptor tanmlar.</li>\n	<li>stenirse devre d braklabilir.\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.jpa.open-in-view=false</code></pre>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Hibernate 5.x i&ccedil;in tercih edilen y&ouml;ntemenable lazy load no trans &ouml;zelliidir.\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<pre>\n<code class=\"language-apache\">spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.enable_lazy_load_no_trans=true</code></pre>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>Sample Data Population</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Spring Boot classpath&#39;de schema.sql ve data.sql script dosyalar mevcut ise bu dosyalarn i&ccedil;indeki sql ifadelerini bootstrap srasnda &ccedil;altracaktr.</li>\n	<li>Dosyalarn lokasyonu veya isimleri uygulamaya g&ouml;re &ouml;zelletirilebilir.\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.datasource.schema=classpath:/schema.sql\nspring.datasource.data=classpath:/data.sql</code></pre>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>Sample Data Population</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Eer classpath&#39;de mevcut ise <strong>schema-$ {platform}.sql </strong>ve <strong>data-${platform}.sql </strong>dosyalarndaki ifadeler de &ccedil;altrlacaktr.</li>\n	<li>${platform} deikeninin deeri application.properties i&ccedil;erisindeki tanmdan &ccedil;&ouml;z&uuml;mlenir,\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.datasource.platform=all\n// hsqldb,h2,oracle,mysql,postgresql gibi deerler yazlabilir. Bizim belirlediimiz bir deerde olabilir</code></pre>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>Sample Data Population</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Hibernate&#39;de bootstrap srasnda eer ddl-auto deeri create veya create-drop durumunda classpath&#39;de import.sql isimli bir dosya mevcut ise bu dosyadaki sql ifadelerini &ccedil;altrr.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>Veritaban Init S&uuml;recindeki lemlerin Sralamas</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>schema-${platform}.sql</li>\n	<li>schema.sql</li>\n	<li>data-${platform}.sql</li>\n	<li>data.sql</li>\n	<li>ddl-auto deerine g&ouml;re schema deiiklikleri</li>\n	<li>ddl-auto deeri create|create-drop ise import.sql</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>Data Initialization&rsquo;n Devre D Braklmas</strong></h3>\n\n<p>stenirse veritaban initialization ilemi devre d braklabilir,&nbsp;</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-apache\">spring.datasource.initialization-mode=never\n// Alabilecei deerler: always, embedded, never</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>DB Migration Destei</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Schema.sql ve data.sql ile veritabannda incremental deiiklikler yaparak ilerlemek m&uuml;mk&uuml;n deildir.</li>\n	<li>Spring Boot gelimi DB migration ihtiya&ccedil;lar i&ccedil;in flyway ve liquibase ara&ccedil;larn desteklemektedir.</li>\n	<li>Flyway dorudan SQL ifadeleri &uuml;zerinden &ccedil;alr.</li>\n	<li>Liquibase ise kendine ait vendor bamsz bir DSL&rsquo;e sahiptir</li>\n	<li>Devreye almak i&ccedil;in ilgili k&uuml;t&uuml;phaneleri pom.xml&rsquo;e eklemek yeterlidir.\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n	&lt;groupId&gt;org.flywaydb&lt;/groupId&gt;\n	&lt;artifactId&gt;flyway-core&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n	&lt;groupId&gt;org.liquibase&lt;/groupId&gt;\n	&lt;artifactId&gt;liquibase-core&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;</code></pre>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>Flyway</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Flyway migration SQL dosyalar classpath&rsquo;de db/migration dizini altna yer almaldr.</li>\n	<li>Dosyalarn format V&lt;version&gt;__&lt;desc&gt;.sql eklinde olmaldr.\n	<ul>\n		<li>V1__schema.sql</li>\n		<li>V2__data.sql</li>\n		<li>...</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Migration ilemleri ile ilgili takip DB&rsquo;de flyway_schema_history isimli tablo i&ccedil;erisinde ger&ccedil;ekletirilir.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>Liquibase</strong></h3>\n\n<p>classpath:/db/changelog/db.changelog-master.yaml</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">databaseChangeLog:\n	- changeSet:\n		id: 1\n		changes:\n			- createTable:\n				tableName: person\n				columns:\n					- column:\n						name: id\n						type: int\n						constraints:\n						primaryKey: true\n						nullable: false\n					- column:\n						name: first_name\n						type: varchar(255)\n	- changeSet:\n		id: 2\n		changes:\n			- addColumn:\n				tableName: person\n				columns:\n					- column:\n						name: last_name\n						type: varchar(255)</code></pre>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'spring-boot-ve-veritabani-islemleri', 'Spring Boot ve Veritaban lemleri', '2cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-16144ef4a27d', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', 'JDBC;JPA;Hibernate'),
                                                                                                       ('1cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-30006ef4a271', '<p>Spring Security kabiliyetlerini devreye almak i&ccedil;in &ouml;ncelikle security starter&#39; tanml olmaldr.</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-apache\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n	&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n	&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-security&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Default olarak b&uuml;t&uuml;n HTTP endpoint&#39;leri g&uuml;venlik altna alnmtr.</li>\n	<li>Default olarak password&#39;&uuml; rastgele belirlenmi ve lNFO log d&uuml;zeyinde console&#39;a yazlan user isimli bir kullanc mevcuttur.</li>\n	<li>Bu kullanc adn ve password&#39;&uuml; ve rollerini application.properties&#39;den deitirmek m&uuml;mk&uuml;nd&uuml;r.\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">security.user.name=user\nsecurity.user.password=secret\nsecurity.user.role=USER,ACTUATOR</code></pre>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>HSTS, XSS, CSRF gibi &ouml;zellikler devreye alnmtr.</li>\n	<li>Default olarak aadaki statik web resource path&#39;leri public resource (unsecure) olarak eriilmektedir.\n	<ul>\n		<li>/css/**</li>\n		<li>/js/**</li>\n		<li>/images/**</li>\n		<li>/webjars/**</li>\n		<li>**/favicon.ico</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>Default Security Konfig&uuml;rasyonu</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Default web app security konfig&uuml;rasyonunu &ouml;zelleitirmek i&ccedil;in <strong>WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter</strong> snfndan t&uuml;reyen bir konfig&uuml;rasyon snf yazlmaldr.</li>\n	<li>Default konfig&uuml;rasyonu tamamen devre d brakmak i&ccedil;in <strong>@EnableWebSecurity</strong> eklenmelidir.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Configuration\n@EnableWebSecurity\npublic class PetClinicSecurityConfig extends WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter {\n...\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>Form Tabanl Login- Overview</strong></h3>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">// http://localhost:8080/login.html\n@Controller\npublic class LoginFormController {\n	@RequestMapping(value=\"/login.html\", method=RequestMethod.GET)\n	public ModelAndView loginPage() {\n		ModelAndView mav = new ModelAndView();\n		mav.setViewName(\"login\");\n		return mav;\n	}\n}\n// application.properties ierisinde\n// spring.mvc.view.prefix=/WEB-INF/jsp/\n// spring.mvc.view.suffix=.jsp</code></pre>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-html\">// /WEB-INF/jsp/login.jsp\n&lt;html&gt;\n	&lt;body&gt;\n		&lt;form action=\"login\" method=\"post\"&gt;\n			Username:&lt;input name=\"username\" type=\"text\" /&gt; &lt;br/&gt;\n			Password:&lt;input name=\"password\" type=\"password\" /&gt; &lt;br/&gt;\n			&lt;input type=\"hidden\" name=\"${_csrf.parameterName}\" value=\"${_csrf.token}\"/&gt;\n			&lt;input type=\"submit\" value=\"Login\"/&gt;\n		&lt;/form&gt;\n	&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>Logout</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Spring Security&rsquo;nin default ayarlarnda logout ve CSRF kabiliyetleri aktiftir.</li>\n	<li>Default logout URI&rsquo; /logout eklindedir.</li>\n	<li>Ancak CSRF, /logout URI&rsquo;na HTTP GET ile eriime izin vermez.</li>\n	<li>Dolays ile logout ilemi i&ccedil;in bir HTML form kullanmak ve POST metodu ile web istei g&ouml;ndermek gerekecektir.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-html\">&lt;html&gt;\n	&lt;body&gt;\n		...\n		&lt;form action=\"logout\" method=\"post\"&gt;\n			&lt;input type=\"submit\" value=\"Logout\"&gt;\n			&lt;input type=\"hidden\" name=\"${_csrf.parameterName}\" value=\"${_csrf.token}\"&gt;\n		&lt;/form&gt;\n	&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>Beni Hatrla</strong></h3>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-html\">&lt;html&gt;\n	&lt;body&gt;\n		...\n		&lt;form action=\"login\" method=\"post\"&gt;\n			Username:&lt;input name=\"username\" type=\"text\" /&gt; &lt;br/&gt;\n			Password:&lt;input name=\"password\" type=\"password\" /&gt; &lt;br/&gt;\n			Remember Me:&lt;input name=\"remember-me\" type=\"checkbox\"&gt; &lt;br/&gt;\n			&lt;inputtype=\"hidden\" name=\"${_csrf.parameterName}\" value=\"${_csrf.token}\"/&gt;\n			&lt;input type=\"submit\" value=\"Login\"/&gt;\n		&lt;/form&gt;\n	&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Configuration\npublic class SecurityConfiguration extends WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter{\n	@Autowired\n	private UserDetailsService userDetailsService;\n	@Override\n	protected void configure(HttpSecurity http) throws Exception {\n		...\n		http.rememberMe().userDetailsService(userDetailsService);\n	}\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>HTTP Basic Auth</strong></h3>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Configuration\npublic class SecurityConfiguration extends WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter {\n	@Override\n	protected void configure(HttpSecurity http) throws Exception {\n		...\n		http.httpBasic();\n	}\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>H2 Console&rsquo;a Eriim</strong></h3>\n\n<p>H2 Console&rsquo;un kendine ait bir authentication mekanizmas olduu i&ccedil;in spring security&rsquo;nin dnda braklmas gerekir</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Configuration\n@Order(value=0)\npublic class H2SecurityConfigurationextends WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter {\n	@Override\n	protected void configure(HttpSecurity http) throws Exception {\n		http.antMatcher(\"/h2-console/**\");\n		http.authorizeRequests().anyRequest().permitAll();\n		http.csrf().disable();\n		http.headers().frameOptions().disable();\n	}\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>Web Kaynaklarnn Yetkilendirilmesi</strong></h3>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Configuration\npublic class SecurityConfiguration extends WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter {\n	@Override\n	protected void configure(HttpSecurity http) throws Exception {\n		http.authorizeRequests()\n			.antMatchers( \"/**/favicon.ico\", \"/css/**\", \"js/**\", \"/images/**\", \"/webjars/**\", \"/login.html\").permitAll()\n			.antMatchers(\"/rest/**\").access(\"hasRole(\'EDITOR\')\")\n			.antMatchers(\"/actuator/**\").access(\"hasRole(\'ADMIN\')\")\n			.anyRequest().authenticated();\n	}\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>Metot D&uuml;zeyinde Yetkilendirme</strong></h3>\n\n<p>Metot d&uuml;zeyinde yetkilendirmeyi devreye almak i&ccedil;in <strong>@EnableGlobalMethodSecurity</strong> anotasyonuna sahip bir konfig&uuml;rasyon snf olmaldr</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@EnableGlobalMethodSecurity(prePostEnabled = true, securedEnabled = true, jsr250Enabled = true)\npublic class PetClinicSecurityConfiguration {\n	...\n}</code></pre>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Service\npublic class PetClinicServiceImpl implements PetClinicService{\n	@PreAuthorize(\"hasAnyRole(\'ROLE_USER\',\'ROLE_EDITOR\')\")\n	public List&lt;Owner&gt; findOwners() {\n		return ownerRepository.findAll();\n	}\n	@PreAuthorize(\"hasRole(\'ROLE_EDITOR\') and hasIpAddress(192.168.1.0/24)\")\n	public void createOwner(Owner owner) {\n		ownerRepository.create(owner);\n	}\n	...\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>Kullanc Bilgilerinin Veritabanndan Alnmas</strong></h3>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Configuration\npublic class SecurityConfiguration extends WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter{\n	...\n	@Autowired\n	private DataSource dataSource;\n\n	@Override\n	protected void configure(AuthenticationManagerBuilder auth) throws Exception {\n		auth.jdbcAuthentication().dataSource(dataSource);\n        // auth.jdbcAuthentication()\n        // .usersByUsernameQuery(usersByUsernameQuery)\n        // .authoritiesByUsernameQuery(authoritiesByUsernameQuery)\n        // .groupAuthoritiesByUsername(groupAuthoritiesByUsername)...\n	}\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>Kriptolu ifre Kullanm</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Spring Security ifrelerin DB&#39;de kriptolu olarak saklanmasn salar.</li>\n	<li>ifreleri kriptolamak i&ccedil;in deiik algoritmalar kullanlabilir.\n	<ul>\n		<li>bcrypt, pbkdf2, scrypt, md4, sha...</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Bunlarn hepsi tek y&ouml;nl&uuml; algoritmalardr.</li>\n	<li>Kimliklendirme srasnda kullancnn girdii ifre algoritmaya g&ouml;re kriptolanarak DB&#39;deki kriptolu deer ile karlatrlr.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>Oturum Y&ouml;netimi</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Tomcat Web Container&rsquo;n session timeout deeri default 30 dk&rsquo;dr.</li>\n	<li>Application.properties i&ccedil;erisinden deitirilebilir.\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">server.session.timeout=60</code></pre>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Configuration\npublic class SecurityConfiguration extends WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter {\n	@Override\n	protected void configure(HttpSecurity http) throws Exception {\n		...\n	}\n	http.sessionManagement()\n		.sessionCreationPolicy(SessionCreationPolicy.IF_REQUIRED)\n		.maximumSessions(1)\n		.maxSessionsPreventsLogin(false)\n		.expiredUrl(\"/login\");\n\n	@Bean\n	public ServletListenerRegistrationBean&lt;HttpSessionEventPublisher&gt;\n	httpSessionEventPublisher() {\n		return new ServletListenerRegistrationBean&lt;HttpSessionEventPublisher&gt;(new HttpSessionEventPublisher());\n	}\n}</code></pre>', 'spring-boot-ve-guvenlik', 'Spring Boot ve Gvenlik', '2cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-16144ef4a27d', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', 'security'),
                                                                                                       ('1cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-30007ef4a271', '<p><a href=\"https://www.testcontainers.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Testcontainers</a>, Docker konteynerlerini JUnit testlerine kolaylkla entegre etmeye izin veren bir Java k&uuml;t&uuml;phanesidir.</p>\n\n<h2>Bamllklar</h2>\n\n<p>Testcontainers&#39; kullanmak i&ccedil;in aadaki bamllklar <code>pom.xml</code>&#39;e eklenmeli (Maven tabanl proje varsaylarak):</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">&lt;properties&gt;\n    &lt;org.testcontainers.version&gt;1.12.5&lt;/org.testcontainers.version&gt;\n&lt;/properties&gt;\n\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;org.testcontainers&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;testcontainers&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;${org.testcontainers.version}&lt;/version&gt;\n    &lt;scope&gt;test&lt;/scope&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;org.testcontainers&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;VERTABANI&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;${org.testcontainers.version}&lt;/version&gt;\n    &lt;scope&gt;test&lt;/scope&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>VERTABANI, postgresql, mysql, mariadb&#39;den biridir.</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>Not: Testcontainers, JUnit 5 (Jupiter) eklentisi salar, ancak bu eklentide sunulan senaryoda gerekli olmayacaktr.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<h2>Veri Kayna Yaplandrmas</h2>\n\n<p>Spring Boot testleri i&ccedil;in Testcontainers&#39; yaplandrma admlar:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Driver&#39; Testcontainers JDBC proxy s&uuml;r&uuml;c&uuml;s&uuml; olan <code>org.testcontainers.jdbc.ContainerDatabaseDriver</code> olarak ayarlanmal. Bunun amac veri kayna balatldnda gerekli Docker konteynerini balatmaktan sorumlu olacaktr.</li>\n	<li>Veritabannz i&ccedil;in diyalekti&nbsp;a&ccedil;k&ccedil;a ayarlanmal&nbsp;aksi takdirde uygulamay balatrken hata alrz. Uygulamada <em>JPA</em> kullandnzda bu adm gereklidir.(<em>Spring Data JPA&nbsp;</em>araclyla)</li>\n	<li>JDBC URL&#39;sini <code>jdbc:tc:&lt;database-image&gt;:&lt;version&gt;:///</code> olarak ayarlanmal&nbsp;b&ouml;ylece Testcontainers hangi veritaban g&ouml;r&uuml;nt&uuml;s&uuml;n&uuml; kullanacan bilir.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>PostgreSQL yaplandrmas:</h3>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-apache\">spring.datasource.driver-class-name=org.testcontainers.jdbc.ContainerDatabaseDriver\nspring.datasource.url=jdbc:tc:postgresql:9.6:///\nspring.jpa.database-platform=org.hibernate.dialect.PostgreSQL9Dialect\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3>MySQL yaplandrmas:</h3>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.datasource.driver-class-name=org.testcontainers.jdbc.ContainerDatabaseDriver\nspring.datasource.url=jdbc:tc:mysql:8:///\nspring.jpa.database-platform=org.hibernate.dialect.MySQL8Dialect\n</code></pre>\n\n<h3>MariaDB yaplandrmas:</h3>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.datasource.driver-class-name=org.testcontainers.jdbc.ContainerDatabaseDriver\nspring.datasource.url=jdbc:tc:mariadb:10.3:///\nspring.jpa.database-platform=org.hibernate.dialect.MariaDB103Dialect\n</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>Veritaban yaplandrmas hakknda daha fazla bilgiyi u adresteki resmi belgelerde bulunabilir: <a href=\"https://www.testcontainers.org/modules/databases/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.testcontainers.org/modules/databases/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<h2>Test veritabann Testcontainers ile&nbsp;balatma</h2>\n\n<p>Veritabann Testcontainers tarafndan y&uuml;klenen komut dosyasyla balatabilirsiniz. Dosya, dorudan snf yolundan veya herhangi bir konumdan y&uuml;klenebilir. Yaplacak tek ey, JDBC URL&#39;sini deitirmektir:</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.datasource.url=jdbc:tc:postgresql:9.6:///?TC_INITSCRIPT=file:src/main/resources/init_db.sql</code></pre>\n\n<p>yada</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">spring.datasource.url=jdbc:tc:postgresql:9.6:///?TC_INITSCRIPT=classpath:init_db.sql\n</code></pre>\n\n<h2>@DataJpaTest</h2>\n\n<p>TC&#39;yi <code>@DataJpaTest</code>&#39;te kullanmak i&ccedil;in, uygulama tanml (otomatik yaplandrlm) veri kaynann kullanldndan emin olmanz gerekir. Testinize, aada g&ouml;sterildii gibi <code>@AutoConfigureTestDatabase</code>&nbsp;ile a&ccedil;klama ekleyerek bunu kolayca yapabilirsiniz:</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@DataJpaTest\n@AutoConfigureTestDatabase(replace = AutoConfigureTestDatabase.Replace.NONE)\npublic class OwnerRepositoryTests {\n\n    @Autowired\n    private OwnerRepository ownerRepository;\n\n    @Test\n    void findAllReturnsJohnDoe() { // as defined in tc-initscript.sql\n        var owners = ownerRepository.findAll();\n        assertThat(owners.size()).isOne();\n        assertThat(owners.get(0).getFirstName()).isEqualTo(\"John\");\n        assertThat(owners.get(0).getLastName()).isEqualTo(\"Doe\");\n    }\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h2>@SpringBootTest</h2>\n\n<p><code>@SpringBootTest</code>, uygulama tanml veri kaynan kullanr, bu nedenle ek deiiklik gerekmez.</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@SpringBootTest(webEnvironment = SpringBootTest.WebEnvironment.RANDOM_PORT)\n@AutoConfigureMockMvc\npublic class OwnerResourceTests {\n\n    @Autowired\n    WebApplicationContext wac;\n\n    @Test\n    void findAllReturnsJohnDoe() throws Exception {\n        given().webAppContextSetup(wac)\n        .when().get(\"/owners\")\n        .then().status(HttpStatus.OK)\n               .body(\"_embedded.owners.firstName\", containsInAnyOrder(\"John\"),\n                     \"_embedded.owners.lastName\", containsInAnyOrder(\"Doe\"));\n    }\n}</code></pre>', 'testcontainers-postgresql-mysql-mariadb', 'Testcontainers / PostgreSQL, MySQL, MariaDB', '2cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-16144ef4a27d', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', 'Testcontainers;PostgreSQL;MySQL;MariaDB');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `body`, `slug`, `title`, `user_id`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `tags`) VALUES
                                                                                                       ('1cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-30008ef4a271', '<p>Testcontainer, verilen Docker Image bilgilerine g&ouml;re ortamda Docker container ayaa kaldrp testlerimize balamamza olanak salayan bir k&uuml;t&uuml;phanedir. &ccedil;eriinde DB, Couchbase, InfluxDB, Elasticsearch, Kafka vb. farkl bileenlerin testleri i&ccedil;in &ouml;nceden hazrlanm ve hale eklenmeye devam eden componentler barndrmakla birlikte docker image name ve version vererek de kendimiz container ayaa kaldrabiliyoruz.</p>\n\n<p>Balca eklememiz gereken k&uuml;t&uuml;phaneler ancak ihtia&ccedil; halinde&nbsp;powermock,&nbsp;jupiter veya junit kullanlabilir.</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n	&lt;groupId&gt;com.github.stefanbirkner&lt;/groupId&gt;\n	&lt;artifactId&gt;system-rules&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n	&lt;version&gt;1.17.2&lt;/version&gt;\n	&lt;scope&gt;test&lt;/scope&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n	&lt;groupId&gt;org.testcontainers&lt;/groupId&gt;\n	&lt;artifactId&gt;testcontainers&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n	&lt;version&gt;1.11.0&lt;/version&gt;\n	&lt;scope&gt;test&lt;/scope&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<p>lk &ouml;nce testlerimizde configurasyon yapacamz custom bir annotation oluturalm ve inceleyelim,</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Target(ElementType.TYPE)\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@ActiveProfiles(value = {\"integration-test\"})\n@ContextConfiguration(\n    initializers = {RabbitMqAwareInitializer.class, RedisContainerConfig.class},\n    classes = IntegrationTestConfig.class\n)\n@RunWith(SpringJUnit4ClassRunner.class)\n@SpringBootTest(webEnvironment = WebEnvironment.MOCK)\n@AutoConfigureMockMvc\npublic @interface SpringBootTestConfig {}</code></pre>\n\n<hr />\n<p><code>@Target</code>: Annotation kullanm araln ayarlar ve ElementType&#39;a g&ouml;re a&ccedil;klama kullanlabilir aralnn numaralandrma k&uuml;mesini belirtir.</p>\n\n<p><code>ElementType.ANNOTATION_TYPE</code>, annotation&#39;n @interface tarafndan yazldn, aksi takdirde bir hata bildirildiini belirtir. Benzer ekilde, yaygn olarak kullanlan <code>ElementType.METHOD</code>, a&ccedil;klamann metod olduu anlamna gelir, aksi takdirde bir hata bildirilir.</p>\n\n<p>ElementType kullanm;</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Tip</td>\n			<td>Annotation scope</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>TYPE</td>\n			<td>Snf, interface veya enum bildirimi</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>FIELD</td>\n			<td>Alan bildirimleri ve enum sabitleri</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>METHOD</td>\n			<td>method</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>PARAMETER</td>\n			<td>parametre</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>CONSTRUCTOR</td>\n			<td>Construction metod</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>LOCAL_VARIABLE</td>\n			<td>Local deiken</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>ANNOTATION_TYPE</td>\n			<td>Annotation tipi (@interface tarafndan deitirilen t&uuml;r)</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>PACKAGE</td>\n			<td>Kurulum paketi beyan</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>TYPE_PARAMETER</td>\n			<td>Tip parametresi bildirimi</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>TYPE_USE</td>\n			<td>Tek tip kullan</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<hr />\n<p><code>@Retention</code>, RetentionPolicy enum t&uuml;r&uuml;n&uuml;n sabitiyle birlikte, yorumun ne kadar s&uuml;reyle tutulmas gerektiini belirtir.&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>RetentionPolicy</code> yorumlar tutmak i&ccedil;in &ccedil;eitli stratejileri a&ccedil;klar.</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n			<td>A&ccedil;klama</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>SOURCE</td>\n			<td>Derleyici yorumu drop eder.</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>CLASS</td>\n			<td>Derleyici dosyada g&uuml;nl&uuml;e kaydedilir ve varsaylan &ccedil;alma zaman sanal makine saklamas gerektirmez.</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>RUNTIME</td>\n			<td>Derleyici bir dosyaya kaydedilir ve kolay okuma i&ccedil;in sanal makine &ccedil;alma zaman tarafndan tutulur.</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<hr />\n<p><code>@ActiveProfiles</code>; Spring integration testinde <code>ApplicationContext</code>&#39;i y&uuml;klerken profilleri etkinletirmek i&ccedil;in kullanlan snf d&uuml;zeyinde bir a&ccedil;klamadr. Aadaki &ouml;zellikleri vardr.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>profiles</strong>: Etkinletirilecek profilleri belirtir.</li>\n	<li><strong>resolver</strong>: Profilleri programl olarak etkinletirmek i&ccedil;in <code>ActiveProfilesResolver</code>&#39; belirtir.</li>\n	<li><strong>value</strong>: <code>profiles</code> &ouml;esinin takma addr</li>\n	<li><strong>inheritProfiles</strong>: Etkin profillerin &uuml;st snftan devralnp devralnmayacana karar veren Boolean deeridir. Varsaylan deeri true.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr />\n<p><code>@ContextConfiguration</code>:</p>\n\n<p>Spring entegrasyonu testi i&ccedil;in bir <code>ApplicationContext</code> y&uuml;kler. <code>ApplicationContext</code>&#39;i XML kayna veya <code>@Configuration</code> ile a&ccedil;klamal JavaConfig kullanarak y&uuml;kleyebilir. Ayrca <code>@Component</code>,&nbsp;<code>@Service</code>,&nbsp;<code>@Repository</code> vb. ile a&ccedil;klamal bir bileenleri y&uuml;kleyebilir. Ayrca <code>javax.inject</code> ile anootated edilmi snflar da y&uuml;kleyebiliriz. Aadaki &ouml;elere sahiptir.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>classes</strong>: <code>@Configuration</code> ile tanmlanm&nbsp;snflar, <code>ApplicationContext</code>&#39;i y&uuml;klemek i&ccedil;in atanr.</li>\n	<li><strong>inheritInitializers</strong>: Test &uuml;st snflarndan balam balatclarn devralnp devralnmayacana karar veren bir Boolean deeri. Varsaylan true</li>\n	<li><strong>inheritLocations</strong>: Test &uuml;st snflarndan resource konumlarnn veya annotate edilmi&nbsp;snflarn devralnp devralnmayacana karar veren Boolean deeri. Varsaylan true</li>\n	<li><strong>initializers</strong>: <code>ConfigurableApplicationContext</code>&#39;i balatan uygulama balam balatc snflarn belirtiriz.</li>\n	<li><strong>loader</strong>: <code>ApplicationContext</code>&#39;i y&uuml;klemek i&ccedil;in <code>ContextLoader</code> veya <code>SmartContextLoader</code> snfmz belirtiyoruz.</li>\n	<li><strong>locations</strong>: <code>ApplicationContext</code>&#39;i y&uuml;klemek i&ccedil;in resource konumlarn belirtiriz.</li>\n	<li><strong>name</strong>: Bu konfig&uuml;rasyon tarafndan temsil edilen balam hiyerari seviyesinin addr.</li>\n	<li><strong>value</strong>: <code>locations</code> &ouml;esinin dier addr.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Bizim &ouml;rneimizde&nbsp;<code>RabbitMqAwareInitializer</code> ve&nbsp;<code>RedisContainerConfig</code> isminde 2 adet balatcmz bulunmaktadr. Ayrca runtime&#39;da&nbsp; loadTimeWeaver bean&#39;i inject etmek i&ccedil;in gerekli snflarmz var.</p>\n\n<p><code>RabbitMqAwareInitializer</code></p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">import com.rabbitmq.client.Channel;\nimport com.rabbitmq.client.Connection;\nimport com.rabbitmq.client.ConnectionFactory;\nimport org.junit.Rule;\nimport org.junit.contrib.java.lang.system.EnvironmentVariables;\nimport org.springframework.boot.test.context.TestConfiguration;\nimport org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextInitializer;\nimport org.springframework.context.ConfigurableApplicationContext;\nimport org.testcontainers.containers.GenericContainer;\nimport java.io.IOException;\nimport java.util.concurrent.TimeoutException;\nimport static org.junit.Assert.assertNotNull;\n\n@TestConfiguration public class RabbitMqAwareInitializer\n    implements ApplicationContextInitializer&lt;ConfigurableApplicationContext&gt; {\n    public static Channel rabbitmq;\n    public static int rabbitmqPort = 5672;\n    public static int rabbitmqManagementPort = 15672;\n\n    public static final GenericContainer&lt;?&gt; rabbitmqContainer;\n    @Rule public static EnvironmentVariables env = new EnvironmentVariables();\n\n    static {\n        rabbitmqContainer = new GenericContainer&lt;&gt;(\"rabbitmq:3.7-management\");\n        rabbitmqContainer.withExposedPorts(rabbitmqPort);\n        rabbitmqContainer.withExposedPorts(rabbitmqManagementPort);\n        rabbitmqContainer.start();\n        env.set(\"RABBIT_HOST\", rabbitmqContainer.getContainerIpAddress());\n        env.set(\"RABBIT_PORT\", String.valueOf(rabbitmqContainer.getMappedPort(rabbitmqPort)));\n        env.set(\"RABBIT_MANAGEMENT_PORT\", String.valueOf(rabbitmqContainer.getMappedPort(rabbitmqManagementPort)));\n        env.set(\"RABBIT_USERNAME\", \"guest\");\n        env.set(\"RABBIT_PASSWD\", \"guest\");\n        ConnectionFactory factory = new ConnectionFactory();\n        factory.setHost(System.getenv(\"RABBIT_HOST\"));\n        factory.setPort(Integer.parseInt(System.getenv(\"RABBIT_PORT\")));\n        factory.setUsername(System.getenv(\"RABBIT_USERNAME\"));\n        factory.setPassword(System.getenv(\"RABBIT_PASSWD\"));\n        try {\n            Connection connection = factory.newConnection();\n            rabbitmq = connection.createChannel();\n        } catch (IOException | TimeoutException e) {\n            e.printStackTrace();\n        }\n        assertNotNull(rabbitmq);\n    }\n    @Override\n    public void initialize(ConfigurableApplicationContext configurableApplicationContext){}\n}</code></pre>\n\n<p><code>RedisContainerConfig</code></p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">import org.junit.Rule;\nimport org.junit.contrib.java.lang.system.EnvironmentVariables;\nimport org.springframework.boot.test.context.TestConfiguration;\nimport org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextInitializer;\nimport org.springframework.context.ConfigurableApplicationContext;\nimport org.testcontainers.containers.GenericContainer;\nimport redis.clients.jedis.Jedis;\nimport java.util.HashMap;\nimport java.util.Map;\nimport static org.junit.Assert.assertNotNull;\n\n@TestConfiguration public class RedisContainerConfig\n    implements ApplicationContextInitializer&lt;ConfigurableApplicationContext&gt; {\n\n    public static Jedis jedis;\n\n    public static int redisPort = 6379;\n\n    public static final GenericContainer&lt;?&gt; redisContainer;\n\n    @Rule public static EnvironmentVariables env = new EnvironmentVariables();\n\n    static {\n        //Configure containers\n        redisContainer = new GenericContainer&lt;&gt;(\"redis:5.0.4\");\n        redisContainer.withExposedPorts(redisPort);\n        redisContainer.start();\n\n        // Configure desired environment variables\n        env.set(\"REDIS_HOST\", redisContainer.getContainerIpAddress());\n        env.set(\"REDIS_PORT\", String.valueOf(redisContainer.getFirstMappedPort()));\n\n        // Configure clients to interact with the containers\n        jedis =\n            new Jedis(System.getenv(\"REDIS_HOST\"), Integer.parseInt(System.getenv(\"REDIS_PORT\")));\n        assertNotNull(jedis);\n    }\n\n    public static void addRedis(String key, Map&lt;String, String&gt; hash) {\n        jedis.hmset(\"key\", \"value\");\n    }\n\n    @Override public void initialize(ConfigurableApplicationContext applicationContext) {}\n}</code></pre>\n\n<p><code>@IntegrationTestConfig</code></p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">import org.springframework.context.annotation.Bean;\nimport org.springframework.context.annotation.ComponentScan;\nimport org.springframework.context.annotation.Configuration;\nimport org.springframework.context.annotation.Profile;\nimport org.springframework.instrument.classloading.InstrumentationLoadTimeWeaver;\n\n@Configuration\n@Profile(\"integration-test\")\n@ComponentScan(value = \"com.app\")\npublic class IntegrationTestConfig {\n    @Bean\n    public InstrumentationLoadTimeWeaver loadTimeWeaver()  throws Throwable {\n        InstrumentationLoadTimeWeaver loadTimeWeaver = new InstrumentationLoadTimeWeaver();\n        return loadTimeWeaver;\n    }\n}</code></pre>\n\n<hr />\n<p><code>@SpringJUnit4ClassRunner</code></p>\n\n<p>Spring&#39;in <strong><em>TestContextManager</em></strong>&#39;n bir JUnit testine yerletiren JUnit4&#39;&uuml;n <em>ClassRunner</em>&#39;nn bir uygulamasdr.</p>\n\n<p><em>TestContextManager</em>, Spring&nbsp;<em>TestContext</em>&nbsp;framework&#39;&uuml;n&uuml;n giri noktasdr ve bu nedenle bir JUnit test snfnda Spring&nbsp;<em>ApplicationContext</em>&nbsp;ve dependency injection&#39;i y&ouml;netir. B&ouml;ylece,&nbsp;<em>SpringJUnit4ClassRunner</em>&nbsp;gelitiricilerin controller&nbsp;ve repository&nbsp;gibi Spring bileenleri i&ccedil;in entegrasyon testleri uygulamasna olanak tanr.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><code>@SpringBootTest</code></p>\n\n<p>Testlerimizde kullanlacak <em>ApplicationContext</em>&#39;i oluturarak &ccedil;alr. &Ccedil;alma&nbsp;ortammz yaplandrmak i&ccedil;in <em>@SpringBootTest</em>&#39;in <em>webEnvironment</em>&nbsp;niteliini kullanabiliriz; kapsaycnn mock bir sunucu uygulamas ortamnda &ccedil;almas i&ccedil;in burada <em>WebEnvironment.MOCK</em> kullanyoruz.</p>\n\n<p>Adndan da anlalaca gibi, entegrasyon testleri, uygulamann farkl katmanlarn entegre etmeye odaklanr. Bu ayn zamanda hi&ccedil;bir mock data olmad anlamna gelir.</p>\n\n<p>deal olarak, entegrasyon testlerini &uuml;nit&nbsp;testlerinden ayr tutmal ve &uuml;nite testleriyle birlikte &ccedil;altrmamalyz. Bunu, yalnzca entegrasyon testlerini &ccedil;altrmak i&ccedil;in farkl bir profil kullanarak yapabiliriz.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><code>@AutoConfigureMockMvc</code>:</p>\n\n<p><code>MockMvc</code>&#39;yi yaplandrmak istediimizde kullanrz.&nbsp;<code>MockMvc</code>&nbsp;ile ilgili t&uuml;m otomatik yaplandrmay etkinletirir.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>Bu tanmlamalardan sonra herhangi integration testini uygulamak istediimiz class yukardaki annotation&#39; tanmlamamz yeterli olacaktr. Spring RabbitMq ve Redis&#39;i local docker&#39;mzda ayaa kaldracaktr.</p>', 'integration-testlerinde-rabbitmq-ve-redis-setup', 'Integration Testlerinde RabbitMq ve Redis Setup', '2cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-16144ef4a27d', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', 'RabbitMq;Redis'),
                                                                                                       ('1cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-30009ef4a271', '<p>Dependency injection, bir uygulamadaki snflar arasnda gevek balant(loose coupling) uygulamaya y&ouml;nelik bir yaklamdr. Bamllklar enjekte etmenin farkl yollar vardr ve bu makale neden yapc enjeksiyonunun tercih edilen yol olmas gerektiini a&ccedil;klamaktadr.</p>\n\n<h2>Dependency injection nedir?</h2>\n\n<p><code>Dependency</code>: Bir nesne, ilemlerini ger&ccedil;ekletirmek i&ccedil;in genellikle dier snflarn nesnelerine ihtiya&ccedil; duyar. Bu nesnelere bamllklar diyoruz.</p>\n\n<p><code>Injection</code>: Bir nesneye gerekli bamllklar salama s&uuml;reci.</p>\n\n<p>Bu nedenle dependency injection, kontrol&uuml;n tersine &ccedil;evrilmesinin (inversion of control, IoC) uygulanmasna yardmc olur. Bu, bamllk nesnelerini oluturan snf yerine, nesne oluturma ve bamllklar enjekte etme sorumluluunun framework&#39;e (yani Spring) verildii anlamna gelir.</p>\n\n<p>Aadakilerle bamllk enjeksiyonu uygulayabiliriz:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>yapc tabanl enjeksiyon(constructor-based),</li>\n	<li>ayarlayc tabanl enjeksiyon(setter-based),</li>\n	<li>alan bazl enjeksiyon(field-based).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Constructor Injection</h2>\n\n<p>Snf i&ccedil;in gereken bamllklar yapcya bamsz deikenler olarak salanr:</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Component\nclass Cake {\n\n  private Flavor flavor;\n\n  Cake(Flavor flavor) {\n    Objects.requireNonNull(flavor);\n    this.flavor = flavor;\n  }\n\n  Flavor getFlavor() {\n    return flavor;\n  }\n  ...\n}</code></pre>\n\n<p>Spring 4.3&#39;ten &ouml;nce, constructor&#39;a bir <code>@Autowired</code> ek a&ccedil;klamas eklememiz gerekiyordu. Daha yeni s&uuml;r&uuml;mlerde, snfn yalnzca bir yapc metodu&nbsp;varsa bu istee baldr. Yukardaki <code>Cake</code>&nbsp;snfnda, yalnzca bir kurucumuz olduundan, <code>@Autowired</code> a&ccedil;klamasn belirtmemize gerek yoktur. Aadaki iki kurucu &ouml;rneini d&uuml;&uuml;n&uuml;n:</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Component\nclass Sandwich {\n\n  private Topping toppings;\n  private Bread breadType;\n\n  Sandwich(Topping toppings) {\n    this.toppings = toppings;\n  }\n\n  @Autowired\n  Sandwich(Topping toppings, Bread breadType) {\n    this.toppings = toppings;\n    this.breadType = breadType;\n  }\n  ...\n}</code></pre>\n\n<p>Birden &ccedil;ok yapc metoda&nbsp;sahip bir snfmz olduunda, <code>@Autowired</code> a&ccedil;klamasn herhangi bir kurucuya a&ccedil;k&ccedil;a eklememiz gerekir, b&ouml;ylece Spring, bamllklar enjekte etmek i&ccedil;in hangi kurucunun kullanlacan bilir.</p>\n\n<h2>Setter Injection</h2>\n\n<p>Gerekli bamllklar snfa alan parametreleri olarak injeckte ediyoruz ve deerler, &ouml;zelliklerin &quot;setter&quot;&nbsp;y&ouml;ntemleri kullanlarak ayarlanyor. Setter metodlarn&nbsp;<code>@Autowired</code> a&ccedil;klama ile a&ccedil;klamalyz. <code>Cake</code> snf, <code>Topping</code> t&uuml;r&uuml;nde bir nesne gerektirir. <code>Topping</code> nesnesi, bu &ouml;zelliin ayarlayc y&ouml;nteminde bir arg&uuml;man olarak salanr:</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Component\nclass Cookie {\n  private Topping toppings;\n\n  @Autowired\n  void setTopping(Topping toppings) {\n    this.toppings = toppings;\n  }\n\n  Topping getTopping() {\n    return toppings;\n  }\n  ...\n}</code></pre>\n\n<p>Spring, <code>@Autowired</code> a&ccedil;klamasn bulacak ve ayarlaycy bamll enjekte etmesi i&ccedil;in &ccedil;aracaktr.</p>\n\n<h2>Field Injection</h2>\n\n<p>Spring, gerekli bamllklar dorudan <code>@Autowired</code> a&ccedil;klama ile a&ccedil;klama ekleme alanlarna atar. Bu &ouml;rnekte, Spring&#39;in <code>Topping</code> bamlln alan enjeksiyonu yoluyla enjekte etmesine izin veriyoruz:</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Component\nclass IceCream {\n  @Autowired\n  private Topping toppings;\n\n  Topping getToppings() {\n    return toppings;\n  }\n\n  void setToppings(Topping toppings) {\n    this.toppings = toppings;\n  }\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h2>Field ve Setter Enjeksiyonlarnn Birleimi</h2>\n\n<p><code>@Autowired</code>&#39; her ikisine de bir alan ve bir ayarlayc eklersek ne olur? Spring, bamll enjekte etmek i&ccedil;in hangi y&ouml;ntemi kullanacak?</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Component\nclass Pizza {\n  @Autowired\n  private Topping toppings;\n\n  Topping getToppings() {\n    return toppings;\n  }\n\n  @Autowired\n  void setToppings(Topping toppings) {\n    this.toppings = toppings;\n  }\n}</code></pre>\n\n<p>Yukardaki &ouml;rnekte, hem &quot;set&quot; fonksiyonuna&nbsp;hem de alana <code>@Autowired</code> a&ccedil;klamasn ekledik. Bu durumda Spring, setter&nbsp;enjeksiyon y&ouml;ntemini kullanarak bamllk enjekte eder. Kodu daha az okunabilir hale getireceinden enjeksiyon t&uuml;rlerini tek bir snfta kartrmann k&ouml;t&uuml; bir uygulama olduunu unutmayn.</p>\n\n<h2>Neden Constructor Injection Kullanmalym?</h2>\n\n<p>Artk farkl enjeksiyon t&uuml;rlerini g&ouml;rd&uuml;&uuml;m&uuml;ze g&ouml;re, yapc enjeksiyon kullanmann baz avantajlarndan ge&ccedil;elim.</p>\n\n<h2>T&uuml;m Gerekli Bamllklar Balatma Zamannda Mevcuttur</h2>\n\n<p>Objeyi yapc metod &ccedil;ardnda olutururuz. Yapc metod gerekli t&uuml;m bamllklar parametre olarak beklerse, o zaman snfn bamllklar enjekte edilmeden asla somutlatrlmayacandan %100 emin olabiliriz.</p>\n\n<p><strong>IoC konteyneri, yapc metoda salanan t&uuml;m arg&uuml;manlarn yapcya aktarlmadan &ouml;nce kullanlabilir olmasn salar.</strong> Bu, k&ouml;t&uuml; &ouml;hretli <code>NullPointerException</code>&#39; &ouml;nlemeye yardmc olur.</p>\n\n<p>Yapc enjeksiyonu son derece kullanldr, &ccedil;&uuml;nk&uuml; gerekli t&uuml;m bamllklarn y&uuml;klenip y&uuml;klenmediini kontrol etmek i&ccedil;in her yerde ayr bir i mant yazmak zorunda olmadmz i&ccedil;in kod karmakl basitletirilir.</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<h4>stee Bal Bamllklar Ne Olacak?</h4>\n\n<p>Ayarlayc(setter) enjeksiyonu ile Spring, bir ayarlayc y&ouml;ntemine <code>@Autowired(required=false)</code> ekleyerek istee bal bamllklar belirlememizi salar. <code>required=false</code> t&uuml;m yapc bamsz deikenlerine uygulanacandan bu, yapc ekleme ile m&uuml;mk&uuml;n deildir.</p>\n\n<p>Java&#39;nn <code>Optional</code> t&uuml;r&uuml;n&uuml; kullanarak yapc enjeksiyonu ile istee bal bamllklar salamaya devam edebiliriz.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<h3>Code Smell&#39;leri tanmlama</h3>\n\n<p>Constructor Injection, beanlerimizin &ccedil;ok fazla baka nesneye baml olup olmadn belirlememize yardmc olur. Kurucumuzun &ccedil;ok sayda arg&uuml;man varsa, bu snfmzn &ccedil;ok fazla sorumluluu olduunun bir iareti olabilir. Sorunlarn uygun ekilde ayrlmasn daha iyi ele almak i&ccedil;in kodumuzu yeniden d&uuml;zenlemeyi d&uuml;&uuml;nmek isteyebiliriz.</p>\n\n<h2>Testlerde Hatalarn &Ouml;nlenmesi</h2>\n\n<p>Yapc enjeksiyonu, birim testleri yazmay basitletirir. Yapc, bizi t&uuml;m bamllklar i&ccedil;in ge&ccedil;erli nesneler salamaya zorlar. Mockito gibi mocking k&uuml;t&uuml;phaneleri kullanarak, daha sonra kurucuya aktarabileceimiz sahte nesneler oluturabiliriz.</p>\n\n<p>Elbette ayarlayclar(setter) araclyla da mock datalar&nbsp;verebiliriz, ancak bir snfa yeni bir bamllk eklersek, testte ayarlaycy &ccedil;armay unutabiliriz, bu da potansiyel olarak testte bir <code>NullPointerException</code>&#39;a neden olur. Yapc enjeksiyonu, test senaryolarmzn yalnzca t&uuml;m bamllklar mevcut olduunda y&uuml;r&uuml;t&uuml;lmesini salar.</p>\n\n<h2>Deimezlik</h2>\n\n<p>Yapc enjeksiyonu, sabit nesneler oluturmaya yardmc olur &ccedil;&uuml;nk&uuml; bir yapcnn imzas, nesneleri oluturmann tek olas yoludur. Bir bean oluturduumuzda, artk bamllklarn deitiremeyiz. Ayarlayc enjeksiyonu ile, oluturulduktan sonra bamll enjekte etmek m&uuml;mk&uuml;nd&uuml;r, bu da dier eylerin yan sra &ccedil;ok i par&ccedil;ackl bir ortamda i par&ccedil;ac g&uuml;venli olmayabilen ve deikenliklerinden dolay hata ayklamas daha zor olan deiken nesnelere yol a&ccedil;ar.</p>\n\n<h2>Sonu&ccedil;</h2>\n\n<p>Constructor injection, kodu daha salam hale getirir. <code>NullPointerException</code>&#39; ve dier hatalar &ouml;nleyerek deimez nesneler oluturmamz salar.</p>', 'neden-constructor-injection-kullanmaliyiz', 'Neden Constructor Injection Kullanmalyz?', '2cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-16144ef4a27d', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', 'Constructor Injection;Setter Injection;Field Injection'),
                                                                                                       ('1cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-30010ef4a271', '<h3><strong>Benzerlikler;</strong></h3>\n\n<p>Vurgulamaya deer ilk nokta, <code>BeanDefinition</code> i&ccedil;in otomatik tarama alglama ve <code>dependency injection</code> ile ilgili olarak t&uuml;m bu annotation&#39;larn (yani, @Component, @Service, @Repository, @Controller) ayn olmasdr. Birini dierinin yerine ksmen kullanabiliriz ve yine de yolumuza devam edebiliriz.</p>\n\n<h3><strong>Farkllklar;</strong></h3>\n\n<h4><strong>@Component</strong></h4>\n\n<p>Bu, snfn bir spring component olduunu belirten genel ama&ccedil;l bir stereotip annotation&#39;dr.</p>\n\n<p>&Ouml;zel olan ey; <code>&lt;context:component-scan&gt;</code>&nbsp;yalnzca <code>@Component</code>&#39;i tarar ve genel olarak <code>@Controller</code>,&nbsp;<code>@Service</code> ve <code>@Repository</code> aramaz. Kendilerine <code>@Component</code> ile annotate edildiinde taranrlar. G&ouml;r&uuml;ld&uuml;&uuml; gibi her <code>@Controller</code>,&nbsp;<code>@Service</code> ve <code>@Repository</code> birer <code>@Component</code>&#39;tr.</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Component\npublic @interface Service {}\n\n@Component\npublic @interface Repository {}\n\n@Component\npublic @interface Controller {}</code></pre>\n\n<p>Bu nedenle <code>@Controller</code>,&nbsp;<code>@Service</code> ve <code>@Repository</code>&#39;nin <code>@Component</code>&#39;in &ouml;zel t&uuml;rleri olduunu s&ouml;ylemek yanl olmaz. <code>&lt;context:component-scan&gt;</code> onlar alr ve takip eden snflarn, sanki <code>@Component</code> ile a&ccedil;klama eklenmi gibi, bean olarak kaydeder. Custom tanmlanm annotation&#39;lar da taranr, &ccedil;&uuml;nk&uuml; kendilerine <code>@Component</code> notu eklenir, bu da <code>@Component</code>&nbsp;olduklar anlamna gelir.</p>\n\n<h4><strong>@Repository</strong></h4>\n\n<p>Bu, snfn bir <code>data repository</code> olduunu belirtmek i&ccedil;indir.&nbsp;<code>DAO</code>&nbsp;(Data Access Objects) denir, DB&#39;ye direkt eriirler.</p>\n\n<p><code>@Repository</code>&#39;nin g&ouml;revi, platforma &ouml;zel istisnalar yakalamak ve bunlar Spring&#39;in birletirilmi denetlenmemi istisnalarndan(unified unchecked exception) biri olarak yeniden atmaktr. Bunun i&ccedil;in, Spring&#39;in uygulama balamna aadaki gibi eklememiz gereken <code>PersistenceExceptionTranslationPostProcessor</code> ile salanr:</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-xml\">&lt;bean class=\"org.springframework.dao.annotation.PersistenceExceptionTranslationPostProcessor\"/&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Bu bean son ilemcisi, <code>@Repository</code> ile a&ccedil;klamal herhangi bir fasulyeye bir danman ekler, b&ouml;ylece platforma &ouml;zg&uuml; istisnalar yakalanr ve ardndan Spring&#39;in denetlenmeyen veri eriimi istisnalarndan biri olarak yeniden g&ouml;nderilir.</p>\n\n<h4><strong>@Controller</strong></h4>\n\n<p>Belirli bir snfn bir controller rol&uuml;ne hizmet ettiini g&ouml;sterir.</p>\n\n<p>Ayn g&ouml;r&uuml;nseler bile, bu ek a&ccedil;klamay <code>@Service</code>&nbsp;veya&nbsp;<code>@Repository</code> gibi bakalaryla deitiremeyiz. Dispatcher, <code>@Controller</code> ile a&ccedil;klamal snflar tarar ve i&ccedil;lerinde&nbsp;<code>@RequestMapping</code> annoationlar alglar ve&nbsp;yalnzca snflar <code>@Controller</code> ile a&ccedil;klamal olan class&#39;larn metodlar ile kullanabiliriz, <code>@Component</code>,&nbsp;<code>@Service</code>,&nbsp;<code>@Repository</code>&nbsp;ile &ccedil;almayacaktr.</p>\n\n<h4><strong>@Service</strong></h4>\n\n<p> mantn tutar ve veri katmanna(repository) giden istekleri y&ouml;netir.</p>\n\n<h4><strong>Sonu&ccedil;</strong></h4>\n\n<p>Yukardakine benzer ekilde, gelecekte Spring, katmanlama kurallarna dayal olarak <code>@Service</code>,&nbsp;<code>@Controller</code>&nbsp;ve&nbsp;<code>@Repository</code> i&ccedil;in &ouml;zel ilevler ekleyebilir. Bu nedenle, projeyi katmanlar dorultusunda kullanmak her zaman iyi bir fikirdir.</p>', 'at-component-vs-at-repository-vs-at-service-vs-at-controller', '@Component vs @Repository vs @Service vs @Controller', '2cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-16144ef4a27d', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', 'Component;Repository;Controller;Service'),
                                                                                                       ('1cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-30011ef4a271', '<h3><strong>Entegrasyon ve Birim Testleri</strong></h3>\n\n<p>Spring Boot, ApplicationContext&#39;i oluturarak &ccedil;alacak entegrasyon ve birim testlerinin yazlmasn da kolaylatrr. Aktive etmek i&ccedil;in test starter&#39;n eklenmesi yeterlidir.</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n	&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n	&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-test&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@RunWith(SpringRunner.class)\n@SpringBootTest\npublic class IntegrationTests {\n	@Autowired\n	private Service service;\n	@Autowired\n	private WebApplicationContext wac;\n	@Test\n	public void testFindOwners() {\n		List&lt;Owner&gt; owners = service.findOwners();\n		MatcherAssert.assertThat(owners.size(), Matchers.equalTo(10));\n	}\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>Entegrasyon Testleri ve REST Servislerine Eriim</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Spring Boot entegrasyon testini &ccedil;altrrken web container&rsquo;da g&ouml;m&uuml;l&uuml; olarak &ccedil;altrabilmektedir.</li>\n	<li>Bu sayede uygulamann web katmanna eriimi engerasyon testleri &uuml;zerinden kontrol etmek m&uuml;mk&uuml;n olmaktadr.</li>\n	<li>Ayrca <strong>TestRestTemplate</strong> isimli yardmc bir snftan bean ile REST servislerine eriim de entegrasyon testlerine tabi tutulabilmektedir.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@RunWith(SpringRunner.class)\n@SpringBootTest(webEnvironment=WebEnvironment.RANDOM_PORT)\npublic class ControllerIntTests {\n	@LocalServerPort\n	private int port;\n\n	@Autowired\n	private TestRestTemplate testRestTemplate; // Spring RestTemplate snfnn zerine ilave kabiliyetler koyar.\n\n	private URL base;\n\n	@Before\n	public void setUp() throws Exception {\n		base = new URL(\"http://localhost:\" + port + \"/welcome\");\n	}\n	@Test\n	public void testWelcome() throws IOException {\n		String response = testRestTemplate.getForObject(base.toString(), String.class);\n		MatcherAssert.assertThat(response, Matchers.containsString(\"Hello World!\"));\n	}\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h3><strong>Mock Mvc ile Controller Metotlarnn Test Edilmesi</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Spring Boot classpath&rsquo;de Servlet API snflar mevcut ise default olarak Mock nesnelerden oluan bir Servlet Container ortam oluturmaktadr.</li>\n	<li>Bu ortam &uuml;zerinden Tomcat gibi herhangi bir web container olmakszn MVC controller metotlar entegrasyon testlerine tabi tutulabilir</li>\n</ul>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@RunWith(SpringRunner.class)\n@AutoConfigureMockMvc\n@SpringBootTest(webEnvironment=WebEnvironment.MOCK)\n// WebApplicationContext\'i Mock Servlet ortam ile oluturur,\n// eer Servlet API snflar classpath\'de mevcut deil ise normal bir ApplicationContext oluturur.\npublic class ControllerUnitTests {\n	@Autowired\n	private MockMvc mvc; //@AutoConfigureMockMvc annotation ile MockMvc nesnesinin otomatik konfigrasyonunu gerekletirir\n\n	@Test\n	public void testWelcome() throws Exception {\n		mvc.perform(MockMvcRequestBuilders.get(\"/hello\")\n			.accept(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON))\n			.andExpect(MockMvcResultMatchers.status().isOk())\n			.andExpect(MockMvcResultMatchers.content()\n			.string(Matchers.containsString(\"Hello World!\")));\n	}\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h2><strong>Mockito.mock()</strong></h2>\n\n<p><code>Mockito.mock()</code>&nbsp;metodu, bir snfn veya bir interface&#39;in&nbsp;mock bir nesnesini oluturmamz salar.</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@Test\npublic void givenCountMethodMocked_WhenCountInvoked_ThenMockedValueReturned() {\n    UserRepository localMockRepository = Mockito.mock(UserRepository.class);\n    Mockito.when(localMockRepository.count()).thenReturn(111L);\n\n    long userCount = localMockRepository.count();\n\n    Assert.assertEquals(111L, userCount);\n    Mockito.verify(localMockRepository).count();\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h2><strong>Mockito&#39;nun&nbsp;@Mock&nbsp;Annotation</strong></h2>\n\n<p>Bu annotation, <code>Mockito.mock()</code>&nbsp;y&ouml;ntemi i&ccedil;in bir ksaltmadr. Ayrca, onu sadece bir test snfnda kullanmalyz. <code>Mockito.mock()</code>&nbsp; y&ouml;nteminden farkl olarak, bu ek a&ccedil;klamay kullanmak i&ccedil;in Mockito annotation&#39;&nbsp;etkinletirmemiz gerekir.</p>\n\n<p>Bunu testi &ccedil;altrmak i&ccedil;in <code>MockitoJUnitRunner</code>&#39; kullanarak veya <code>MockitoAnnotations.initMocks() </code>y&ouml;ntemini a&ccedil;k&ccedil;a &ccedil;ararak yapabiliriz. <code>MockitoJUnitRunner</code> kullanan bir &ouml;rnee bakalm:</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@RunWith(MockitoJUnitRunner.class)\npublic class MockAnnotationUnitTest {\n\n    @Mock\n    UserRepository mockRepository;\n\n    @Test\n    public void givenCountMethodMocked_WhenCountInvoked_ThenMockValueReturned() {\n        Mockito.when(mockRepository.count()).thenReturn(123L);\n\n        long userCount = mockRepository.count();\n\n        Assert.assertEquals(123L, userCount);\n        Mockito.verify(mockRepository).count();\n    }\n}</code></pre>\n\n<p>Kodu daha okunakl hale getirmenin yan sra, <code>@Mock</code>, bir problem durumunda problem&#39;i&nbsp;alan ad hata mesajnda g&ouml;r&uuml;nd&uuml;&uuml; i&ccedil;in bulmay kolaylatrr&nbsp;</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-bash\">Wanted but not invoked:\nmockRepository.count();\n-&gt; at org.baeldung.MockAnnotationTest.testMockAnnotation(MockAnnotationTest.java:22)\nActually, there were zero interactions with this mock.\n\n  at org.baeldung.MockAnnotationTest.testMockAnnotation(MockAnnotationTest.java:22)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Ayrca <code>@InjectMocks</code>&nbsp;ile birlikte kullanldnda, kurulum kodu miktarn &ouml;nemli &ouml;l&ccedil;&uuml;de azaltabilir.</p>\n\n<h2><strong>@MockBean&nbsp;Annotation</strong></h2>\n\n<p>Spring uygulama balamna mock nesneler eklemek i&ccedil;in <code>@MockBean</code>&nbsp;kullanabiliriz. Mock nesne, uygulama balamnda ayn t&uuml;rden herhangi bir mevcut bean&#39;nin yerini alacaktr.</p>\n\n<p>Ayn t&uuml;rden bir bean tanmlanmamsa, yeni bir tane eklenecektir. Bu a&ccedil;klama, belirli bir bean&#39;nin&nbsp;mock edilmesi gereken entegrasyon testlerinde kullanldr. Bu a&ccedil;klamay kullanmak i&ccedil;in, testi &ccedil;altrmak &uuml;zere <code>SpringRunner</code>&#39; kullanmalyz:</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code class=\"language-java\">@RunWith(SpringRunner.class)\npublic class MockBeanAnnotationIntegrationTest {\n\n    @MockBean\n    UserRepository mockRepository;\n\n    @Autowired\n    ApplicationContext context;\n\n    @Test\n    public void givenCountMethodMocked_WhenCountInvoked_ThenMockValueReturned() {\n        Mockito.when(mockRepository.count()).thenReturn(123L);\n\n        UserRepository userRepoFromContext = context.getBean(UserRepository.class);\n        long userCount = userRepoFromContext.count();\n\n        Assert.assertEquals(123L, userCount);\n        Mockito.verify(mockRepository).count();\n    }\n}</code></pre>\n\n<p>Annotation&#39; bir alanda kullandmzda, uygulama balamnda kaytl olmann yan sra, sahte alana da enjekte edilecektir. Bu, yukardaki kodda belirgindir.</p>\n\n<p>Burada, <code>count</code> y&ouml;ntemini saplamak i&ccedil;in enjekte edilen <code>UserRepository</code> mock&#39;unu kullandk. Daha sonra, ger&ccedil;ekten mock bean olduunu dorulamak i&ccedil;in uygulama balamndaki bean&#39;i kullandk.</p>', 'spring-boot-ve-test', 'Spring Boot ve Test', '2cb9374e-4e52-4142-a1af-16144ef4a27d', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', '2022-09-09 10:40:45', 'test;mock;MockBean');
